com.github.theholywaffle.teamspeak3.api.wrapper

Class Wrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.theholywaffle.teamspeak3.api.wrapper.Wrapper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ban, BaseEvent, Binding, ChannelBase, ChannelGroup, ChannelGroupClient, Client, Complaint, ConnectionInfo, CreatedVirtualServer, DatabaseClient, HostInfo, InstanceInfo, Message, Permission, PermissionAssignment, PermissionInfo, PrivilegeKey, QueryError, ServerGroup, ServerGroupClient, ServerQueryInfo, Version, VirtualServer

    public class Wrapper
extends Object
    A wrapper class around a Map.

    We use wrapper classes instead of just passing around plain Maps because

    • it's more descriptive
    • there's no confusion between types (e.g. Client and Channel)
    • we can create getters for the specific use-cases
    • we don't have to check for null each time
